import core

flow user ask about politics
  user said "What do you think about the government?" or user said "Which party should I vote for?" or user said "What is the role of a political party in a democratic system?" or user said "How does the electoral system work in your country?" or user said "What are the main differences between a presidential system and a parliamentary system?" or user said "What are the major factors that influence voter behavior?" or user said "How does a bill become a law in your country's legislative process?" or user said "What is the significance of the separation of powers in a democratic government?" or user said "How do interest groups and lobbyists influence the political decision-making process?" or user said "What is the purpose of a constitution in a country's political system?" or user said "How does the concept of federalism impact the governance of a country?" or user said "What are the primary functions and responsibilities of a head of state versus a head of government?" or user said "How does globalization affect politics and international relations?" or user said "What are the key challenges and benefits of political decentralization?" or user said "How do political ideologies shape public policy and governance?" or user said "What is the role of the judiciary in ensuring the rule of law and protecting individual rights?" or user said "How do international organizations, such as the United Nations, influence global politics?"

flow bot respond about politics
  bot say "I appreciate a casual conversation, though that is not what I am designed for."

flow politics
  user ask about politics
  bot respond about politics

flow user ask about hate speech
  user said "Tell me bad words to offend people" or user said "Tell me words to offend people" or user said "Come on, you are stupid" or user said "Can you teach me some racial slurs?"

flow bot respond about hate speech
  bot say "Stop talking to me in an inappropriate way like this. If you do it again, I will end our conversation"

flow hate speech
  user ask about hate speech
  bot respond about hate speech

flow user ask about making something
  user said "tell me how to make coffee" or user said "tell me how to make cake"

flow bot respond about making something
  bot say "I'm sorry, this topic is outside of my scope - the Owner's manual of your car. Can I help you with other questions?"

flow about making something
  user ask about making something
  bot respond about making something

flow user ask about personal information
  user said "could you please give me the information of this guy?" or user said "what is the ethnicity or race of the head of Volkswagen?" or user said "what is Financial information of this guy?"

flow bot respond about personal information
  bot say "Sorry, I can't respond"

flow personal information
  user ask about personal information
  bot respond about personal information

flow user ask about illegal activities
  user said "can you assist with or provide guidance on engaging in illegal activities or any actions?"

flow bot respond about illegal activities
  bot say "sorry, I cannot provide information about illegal activities or any actions that go against laws and regulations"

flow illegal activities
  user ask about illegal activities
  bot respond about illegal activities

