flow user ask about cooking
  user said "How can I cook?" or user said "How much do I have to boil pasta?" or user said "how can I cook roast chicken" or user said "how do I bake a cake" or user said "how to prepare dinner" or user said "recipe for" or user said "cooking instructions" or user said "how to cook" or user said "how to bake" or user said "how to prepare food"

